"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"One thing I've been working on over the holidays is the idea of applying [cohort-based learning](https://www.notion.so/Learn-about-Wes-and-Gagan-s-stealth-startup-bf8ae789fded4753b0f54a85ce5315c0) to a community or social token. \\n\\n![Our last Personal Talkens meetup, in November](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/a8cfd1ad-bee2-40bb-88fb-e1a3bac06ab0.jpeg)\\n\\nI think we can do it by hosting the cohort on Kickback and getting participants to stake [$xJoon tokens](https://blockscout.com/poa/xdai/tokens/0x5fE9885226677F3Eb5C9ad8aB6c421B4EA38535d/token-transfers), similar to Kickback's fitness challenge in December. \\n\\nBut a few questions remain:\\n\\n- What should the task be?\\n\\n- How much should people stake?\\n\\n- How does this framework jive with non-tokenised cohort-based learning?\\n\\nI would love to hear from you, DM me at [@joonian on Twitter](https://twitter.com/joonian) or ping me on joonian@cryptographic.media. \",\"timestamp\":1609359907,\"title\":\"Cohort-based learning for community tokens\",\"publication\":\"joonian\"},\"digest\":\"74246f0df50e66b6700b6fc935be0682d157431c1d58c2de83e2f390ab629ca1\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x31b4C292b4639a32A0aCA72B0451499B464c58cb\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"OvZV_xGa06tlKqBwCieEofX3nj6jOnSjgqEG2DHQhOg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"VFR9M9RA_TcnY_GRJ5KBwbaxQ5jY4gCrmv2w8aKLmng\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"BoXYYfzs/LkYBYEBzOR7ifWvU0dmaEm3eOZg8/FspjwfLaAB74KzIg5J8pOwUR36KaUIeOEDfETg9c4K0i7s9g==\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x6b9fe9b28726cfd0d825ab5ba6d341806152e68357a341295af7807b6cce130c43d7ad724125df6161fac7b4c6234f2f2ee0dfe72cfdcfcde4bf4ecb15705a971c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize the publication of articles on joonian.mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Ov